title: Grateful Dead Live at Frost Amphitheatre on 1986-05-10
description:
Set 1

Bertha-> Greatest Story Ever Told, West L.A. Fadeaway, Desolation Row, Tennessee Jed, Minglewood Blues, Big Railroad Blues, Let It Grow

Set 2

Hell In A Bucket-> Sugaree, Estimated Prophet-> Eyes Of The World-> Drums-> The Wheel-> China Doll-> Throwing Stones-> Turn On Your Love Light, E: The Mighty Quinn

reviews.review_text: Effing beautiful One of the best Auds out there. My first tape. I love every note.
